metadata.name: Devil Banners #1
metadata.description: ψ Devil Banners ψ is a dark ode to the banners NFT collection, centering around edgy, devilish, black-hearted, and gothcore aesthetics. Devil Banners primarily draws inspiration from the depths of the sinister Remilia ecosystem: community members of Milady, Remilio, Yayo and their project descendants ↜ (╰ • ω •) ╯

attributes.value: This devil tempts you with promises of pleasure and leads you astray
